<P>THE WIDOW's VOW.</P>
<P>A FARCE, IN TWO ACTS, AS IT IS ACTED AT THE THEATRE ROYAL, <HI>HAY-MARKET,</HI> AND BY THE OLD AMERICAN COMPANY, <HI>NEW-YORK.</HI></P>
<P><HI>LONDON</HI>: Printed: <HI>NEW-YORK:</HI> Re-Printed by H. GAINE, the BIBLE, in HANOVER-SQUARE, M, DCC, LXXXVII.</P>
